v0.44.0: calmer food (less screen clutter)

- cut food density (~150 vs 260 default, lower cap + regrow) so pellets read as scattered flora, not a carpet
- pellets are smaller, softer green, and barely emissive so bloom no longer turns them into glowing orbs that dominate the biome
- slightly higher energy per pellet to keep the ecosystem balanced; raise the Food lever if you want more
